title: Very moist carrot cake
ingredients: ['For the cake', '250g plain flour', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '350g caster sugar', '225ml vegetable oil', '3 eggs', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '225g grated carrots', '75g desiccated coconut', '120g chopped walnuts', '1 (227g) tin crushed pineapple, drained and pureed', 'For the icing', '225g cream cheese', '50g butter, softened', '250g icing sugar']
